# pppoker.pro

Next.js 15 static export (`apps/web/out`) for Nuts PPPoker. Content from WordPress/Elementor HTML extract. Strangler Fig: native React chrome + legacy Elementor bodies.

**Read `AGENTS.md` in repo root for full guide.**

## Must remember

- Blog list component: `NativeBlogArchive` — never `BlogArchive` / `PostArticle` (audit fails)
- Home blog: inject before `next build`; slot `#native-home-blog-slot`; routes in `elementor-chrome.json` → `homeBlogSlotRoutes`
- `PageShell`: `structuredPost` | `nativeBlog` | legacy `WordPressBody`; Elementor JS only if `page.needsElementorRuntime`
- Branches: `cursor/<name>-3d19`; merge via PR; run `npm run build` before done
- Elementor IDs / contacts: `apps/web/src/config/site.ts`, `elementor-chrome.json`

## Build

`npm run build` = extract → split/inject → verify → next export → flatten RU → verify:* → smoke:homepage
